{"tid":1118481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 傳森美咒安仔Sammi離婚","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T17:03:50.000Z","uid":227275,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf506fec1006d864dc4864ea09b6d73472311f5","tid":1118481,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2F1110.jpg&h=5e1adff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2013年底鄭秀文同許志安傳婚訊，後來證實只係求婚階段，森美再口出狂言：「我起初以為佢哋結婚，原來係求婚成功。我睇穿佢哋計劃，就係求婚時鄭秀文出碟，訂婚時就許志安出碟，鄭秀文開演唱會就係結婚，許志安開演唱會就係離婚，再懷孕就二人一齊開演唱會，呢種宣傳技倆萬試萬靈！」<br />\n結果遭網民狠批口不擇言，得知禍從口出後，佢立即於微博道歉補鑊：「看到報導才發現我所說的意思是那麼的不對，原意是什麼也不重要，任何戲言也以不令人誤會並影響他人為前題。對此事我感到萬分歉意，望鄭秀文小姐和許志安先生及愛他們的所有朋友見諒。現肉袒負荆，公開謝罪。」"},{"pid":"840e95aec9515360d75b10c9867ce22719acf952","tid":1118481,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf0d594f40daae9ed432289f42972427773b4a3","tid":1118481,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"中曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a328f9acb26d9b1912b4731600785fac7a6759c","tid":1118481,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"預言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114a0ff4336201465efa84e43a2fcb25b3fa1ed0","tid":1118481,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"平時咁串 今次唔敢出聲"},{"pid":"1e73edb58a01508573e9ecb528486fc5a35093ae","tid":1118481,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":